# * experiment (required)           - MLflow experiment path
# * registered_model (required)     - Registered model name (for lineage)
# * model_alias (required)          - Model alias (for lineage)
# * eval_threshold_mode (required)  - "relaxed" or "strict"
# * eval_table (optional)           - Evaluation dataset table name
# * git_source_info (optional)      - Git provenance injected by the bundle
##################################################################################

